Program: Outlook
Title: East Timor Violence
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p03kbr4d
Last Broadcast Date: Not available
Isabella Ferrer and investigations into atrocities committed in East Timor. Also, is the suit, the 'uniform of the business world', on the way out? And, Orania, the Afrikaner-only community in South Africa objecting to municipal boundary changes. Presented by Frederick Dove